# The layout observation scene: no assertions on geometry — the harness
# cannot see layout yet, so this scene exists to be recorded and looked
# at (KAYA_RECORD=1). The two expects only prove the tree built end to
# end and clear the zero-expect guard; label#4 is the deepest-nested
# label, so reading it proves nesting reached the leaf.
expect label#0 "Layout probe"
expect label#4 "deep"
